div.div:
Reservation & Parking System Design
Parking Garage
Requirement
- reserve parking spot and receive an ticket.
- pay for the parking spot.
- high consistency : not to reserve the same spot at the same time
- vehicle type : compact, regular, large
-flat rate : based on time , depending on the spot type
- API : public endpoint, internal endpoint

div.div:
Scale :
on a per garage basis, even if we have upper bound, garage have optimisctically 10 floors
let's say there's maybe 200 spots per floor, so 2000 relevant spots per garage - no scale issue
- not concerned about designing this as a distributed system.
-focus on real time design
- avoid race condition (allocate same spot at the same time.)
